{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"40ef32ed-b1ef-4232-92ec-a2a7080062bf","content":"No existing files found — so this is a guidance question rather than a refactoring task. Here's exactly what to do:\n\n### 1. Add `x:DataType` to your XAML\n\nIn `SettingsPage.xaml`, add the `x:DataType` attribute on the root `ContentPage` element, pointing to your ViewModel's CLR type:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n\n        <Entry Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" Placeholder=\"Theme\" />\n\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n\n        <Stepper Value=\"{Binding FontSize}\" Minimum=\"8\" Maximum=\"48\" />\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize, StringFormat='Font Size: {0}'}\" />\n\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\nThat's it — every `{Binding}` under the element with `x:DataType` is now **compiled**.\n\n### 2. Catch binding errors at build time\n\nAdd this to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <!-- Treat broken compiled bindings as build errors -->\n  <MauiStrictXamlCompilation>true</MauiStrictXamlCompilation>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\nWith this enabled, if you typo a property (e.g., `{Binding Fontsiz}`), the build will **fail** with an error like:\n\n```\nXC0045: Binding: Property \"Fontsiz\" not found on \"SettingsViewModel\"\n```\n\n### Key points\n\n- `x:DataType` can be set on **any** element, not just the root — useful when a child binds to a different type (e.g., inside a `DataTemplate`).\n- To **opt out** for one binding, use `x:DataType=\"\"` or the classic `{Binding Path=Foo, x:DataType={x:Null}}`.\n- Compiled bindings also improve **runtime performance** by avoiding reflection.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"d367141e-7d1b-4bf0-a727-fa8ddf03f10b","outputTokens":576},"id":"59691656-267b-4a8b-8192-e2891a0ea071","timestamp":"2026-04-05T00:59:18.574Z","parentId":"c7cba187-2d5b-4ec6-9aa7-c1d8aed6a9a3"}
